 result←url (show_pass Test) ns;DoTest;suite;tests
 tests⌿⍨←'Test'∘(⊃⍷)¨tests←'T'ns.⎕NL ¯3
 suite←⍕ns
 result←1
 DoTest←{
     F←ns⍎⍵
     0::0⊣⎕←'**TEST ERROR** ',suite,'.',⍵
     0=F url:0⊣⎕←'**TEST FAIL** ',suite,'.',⍵
     ⍺←0
     ⍺:1⊣⎕←'TEST PASS ',suite,'.',⍵
     1
 }
